msgstr "ບັນທຶກຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ເພື່ອສ້າງໂອກາດໃໝ່."

#. module: crm_mail_plugin
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/crm_mail_plugin/static/src/to_translate/translations_outlook.xml:0
